description: Async synchronization primitives, async collections, TPL and dataflow extensions. The JoinableTaskFactory allows synchronously blocking the UI thread for async work. This package is applicable to any .NET application (not just Visual Studio).
releaseNotes: The library now uses a 15.6.0.0 assembly version to be compatible with Visual Studio 15.7 and to reflect that no additional API was added since the 15.6 package version. Note that earlier versions of the 15.7 package used an assembly version of 15.7.0.0.
